column5: Late last night we were moved to a new server. Apparently we were taking up a bit too much resources on the other server and causing some issues.  I've often complained about bigger sites sucking up all the resources and have never been part of the one doing it before now. It was merely a coincidence that this happened right after Irishfield had access to a computer.
I don't suppose you 'forgot' to leave him our forwarding address?
Poor Wayne   got to love the guy I guess that's why we pick on him so much  Whopper
